# Slot Blocking and Patient Notification API Tests
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or copy to Postman/Thunder Client

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@patientToken = YOUR_PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS - Slot Blocking
### ============================================

### 1. Block a Single Slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinician_id": 1,
  "centre_id": 1,
  "date": "2024-12-25",
  "start_time": "10:00:00",
  "end_time": "10:30:00",
  "reason": "Doctor on emergency leave"
}

### 2. Block Multiple Slots
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block-multiple
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slots": [
    {
      "clinician_id": 1,
      "centre_id": 1,
      "date": "2024-12-25",
      "start_time": "11:00:00",
      "end_time": "11:30:00"
    },
    {
      "clinician_id": 1,
      "centre_id": 1,
      "date": "2024-12-25",
      "start_time": "11:30:00",
      "end_time": "12:00:00"
    }
  ],
  "reason": "Doctor unavailable for morning shift"
}

### 3. Block Entire Day for Clinician
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block-day
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinician_id": 1,
  "centre_id": 1,
  "date": "2024-12-26",
  "reason": "Doctor on planned leave"
}

### 4. Get Affected Patients (Preview before blocking)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/affected-patients
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slots": [
    {
      "clinician_id": 1,
      "centre_id": 1,
      "date": "2024-12-25",
      "start_time": "14:00:00",
      "end_time": "14:30:00"
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Get All Blocked Slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/blocked
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Get Blocked Slots with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/blocked?clinician_id=1&date_from=2024-12-01&date_to=2024-12-31&is_blocked=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Unblock a Slot (replace :slotId with actual ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/unblock/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### PATIENT ENDPOINTS - Notifications
### ============================================

### 8. Get Patient Notifications (All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### 9. Get Unread Notifications Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications?unread_only=true&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### 10. Get Notifications with Date Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications?date_from=2024-12-01&date_to=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### 11. Get Unread Notification Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### 12. Mark Notification as Read (replace :notificationId with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### ============================================
### ERROR SCENARIOS - Testing Validation
### ============================================

### 13. Try to Block Past Slot (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinician_id": 1,
  "centre_id": 1,
  "date": "2023-01-01",
  "start_time": "10:00:00",
  "end_time": "10:30:00",
  "reason": "Testing past date validation"
}

### 14. Try to Block with Invalid Time Range (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinician_id": 1,
  "centre_id": 1,
  "date": "2024-12-25",
  "start_time": "10:30:00",
  "end_time": "10:00:00",
  "reason": "Testing invalid time range"
}

### 15. Try to Block Same Slot Twice (Should Fail on Second Attempt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clinician_id": 1,
  "centre_id": 1,
  "date": "2024-12-27",
  "start_time": "15:00:00",
  "end_time": "15:30:00",
  "reason": "Testing duplicate blocking"
}

### 16. Try to Access Admin Endpoint without Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/slots/blocked

### 17. Try to Access Patient Endpoint without Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient/notifications
